        "subject": "LU-5044 llite: .lustre should not be return by readdir",
        "message": "LU-5044 llite: .lustre should not be return by readdir\n\nSkip .lustre in readdir, otherwise some of backup or\nfilesystem scanning tools might go into .lustre and\nread all files under .lustre, which could cause problems.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4339403f74f7981f3ff8d4496d6e6c5cc499ea60\n"
      },
